query:
select l_extendedprice, l_discount
from orders, lineitem
where o_orderkey = l_orderkey
    and o_orderdate < date '1995-03-15'
    and l_shipdate > date '1995-03-15'

FROM public.o_p1,
public.l_p3
WHERE o_p1.o_orderkey = l_p3.l_orderkey AND o_p1.o_orderdate < DATE '1995-03-15' AND l_p3.l_shipdate > generalize_date(DATE '1995-03-15', 'MONTH')
